    "The enhanced prompt achieved one more successful assertion than the simple prompt, but it is unclear if this was caused by the prompt instructions.",
    "Testing this block thoroughly requires reflecting its time behavior in the test programs.GEN SIN: Based on the standard sinus function, this function block generates a sine wave with a programmable period.",
    "Despite simple control flow logic, the calculated output signal values are time-dependent and therefore difficult for an LLM to estimate.",
    "Consequently, in this case, all assertions from the simple and enhanced prompt failed.",
    "However, the enhanced prompt yielded a higher statement coverage in this case, which is illustrated in Fig. 5."
